# Markdown Documentation

## Headings
- `#` for page title, `##` for main sections, `###` for subsections

## Links
- Internal: `[text](path)` with relative paths (e.g. `[Guide](guide/)`)
- External: full URL

## Code
- Fenced blocks: ` ```language` with language tag
- Inline: `` `code` ``

## Other
- Use lists, tables, and emphasis consistently
- Keep paragraphs short; use bullet points for scannability
